data.description: Since listing, Sellers have painted the primary bedroom and the walkout finished area of the basement, installed new flooring in main bathroom and a countertop dishwasher.  This charming three-bedroom ranch home, nestled on 7.3 acres of land, features a picturesque stream running through the property and an inviting in-ground pool. Inside, you'll be enchanted by the warm and welcoming ambiance of the living room and kitchen, complete with a double-sided fireplace.  The upper deck offers a peaceful space and beautiful view of your property.  The walkout basement provides an additional 850 square feet of finished space, excellent for entertaining guests or unwinding.
